; Test commodity comparison with different prices (same currency)
; Covers commodity.cc (price less/greater comparison)

2024/01/15 Buy lot 1
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL {$150}
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/20 Buy lot 2
    Assets:Stocks    5 AAPL {$160}
    Assets:Cash

test bal --lots --no-total Assets:Stocks
      10 AAPL {$150}
       5 AAPL {$160}  Assets:Stocks
end test
